commit.title: Fixes #12428: extracting inlined constants was ignoring signature.
commit.message:
Fixes #12428: extracting inlined constants was ignoring signature.

We ensure that when a signature is given, we don't drop the definition
of an inlined constant in the implementation, since it has to be
needed in the signature.

Note that a non-exported constant cannot be inlined (which is also a
bug per se, or at least a limitation).
